msgid "Are links marked \"safe\" guaranteed to be safe?"
msgstr "Are links marked \"safe\" guaranteed to be safe?"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/components/faq/Content.tsx:36
msgid "We assess risk via the Google Web Risk API, but undetected threats or errors may occur, so absolute safety cannot be guaranteed. Details: https://cloud.google.com/web-risk/docs/overview"
